casebody.data:
Thursday, December 10, 1998

DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

98-401. Toledo Bar Assn. v. Lockhart.

On December 7, 1998, respondent filed an affidavit of compliance. The certificate of service for the affidavit of compliance does not show service upon relator, Toledo Bar Association, as required by S.Ct.Prac.R. XIV(2XA). Accordingly,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that respondent’s affidavit of compliance be, and hereby is, stricken.
